{
  "id": "6a16efe12e27f1c3087aab81",
  "title": "教養とリベラルアーツのIFF性",
  "created": 1779888114,
  "updated": 1779888135,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a16efe12e27f1c3087aab81",
      "text": "教養とリベラルアーツのIFF性",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888114,
      "updated": 1779888115
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff30000000000ed4383",
      "text": "[tokoroten.icon]のClaudeの会話ログから自動生成された記事",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888115,
      "updated": 1779888129
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16f0000000000000ed43a2",
      "text": "----",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888129,
      "updated": 1779888129
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4384",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4385",
      "text": "[ジャーゴンはIFFとして機能する] の拡張。 「教養」「リベラルアーツ」もある種の IFF として機能する。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4386",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4387",
      "text": "[*** 機能のyes側]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4388",
      "text": "\t古典的テキスト・哲学・高文化への言及 = 「私はこの集団に属する」というシグナル",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4389",
      "text": "\tヨーロッパ・日本両方で、古典教育は明示的にエリートの地位と結びついていた",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed438a",
      "text": "\t「教養がある」と他者を評価する語法、フーコーやドストエフスキーへの軽口的言及 = [* 専門ジャーゴンと同じゲートキープ機能]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed438b",
      "text": "\tレファレンスを認識できない人 = よそ者マーク",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed438c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed438d",
      "text": "[*** 反論側 (考慮価値あり)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed438e",
      "text": "\tリベラルアーツの本来の目的は「informed citizens を作る」(階級境界の維持ではない)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed438f",
      "text": "\tただこの目的と機能は [* 両立しうる] (Bourdieu の文化資本論)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4390",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4391",
      "text": "[*** 真の洞察 (両立する二重機能)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4392",
      "text": "Bourdieu の核心: 文化資本の価値は [* 「思考を豊かにする」 + 「集団帰属をマークする」] の二重機能から生じる。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4393",
      "text": "原ツイートの分析は成立する:",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4394",
      "text": "\t教養を持つ側は内輪/外様シグナリングを意識しない可能性大",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4395",
      "text": "\t教養を持たない側は確実にそう受け取る",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4396",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4397",
      "text": "[*** 日本の文脈]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4398",
      "text": "大正期: 西洋哲学が elite の地位マーカーに",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed4399",
      "text": "教養主義 / 知識人 の概念 = 知的ゲートキーパー",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed439a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed439b",
      "text": "[*** マンガ「ようこそFACTへ」の鋭さ]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed439c",
      "text": "「IFFとしての教養」を残酷に描く。 ところてんの直感:",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed439d",
      "text": "\t教養から排除された人 (Watanabe型) は陰謀論に脆弱になる",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed439e",
      "text": "\t陰謀論 = 反知識として in-group メンバーシップをシグナル化、選ばれた感を与える",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed439f",
      "text": "\tIFFの議論直結 — 真実 vs 偽の知識ではなく、[* 位置取りそのものが社会的に重要]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed43a0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16eff40000000000ed43a1",
      "text": "→ 関連: [客観情報が乏しい集団の必然帰結] (B: メタ言語が帰属試験紙化)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888116,
      "updated": 1779888116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16f0050000000000ed43a4",
      "text": "----",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888133,
      "updated": 1779888135
